## Auth Pattern

[Document your exact authentication pattern so Claude never deviates. If you use a non-standard approach, explain why and show the correct code.]

```typescript
// CORRECT — always use this pattern in server components and API routes
// [Adjust this to match your actual auth system]

const cookieStore = await cookies();
const userId = cookieStore.get('user_id')?.value;
if (!userId) redirect('/login');

const { data: user } = await db
  .from('users')
  .select('role, workspace_id')
  .eq('id', userId)
  .single();
```

