## Self-Verification

After writing code, ALWAYS run these commands and fix any errors before marking work complete:

```bash
# Type check (required)
npx tsc --noEmit

# Build check (required — skip in worktrees if env vars unavailable)
npm run build

# [Any project-specific checks]
# e.g.: npm run lint
# e.g.: npm test
```

**Worktree note:** If build fails due to missing environment variables, `npx tsc --noEmit` is the minimum gate.

